data.description: Take advantage of this fantastic opportunity in the heart of Glendale! NO HOA! This spacious home, on a huge corner cul-de-sac lot, offers 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths and can easily accommodate a single family or ''multi-generational'' living! Cozy gated courtyard entry and low maintenance landscaping! The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a large covered patio and a gorgeous 8 ft diving pool, which was recently resurfaced and had a new filter installed. The HVAC systems are only 5 years old! Convenient RV gate makes it easy to park your toys! Great location, close to shopping and dining!
